docs.lead_paragraph: HER name is Furlong, and her two hundred and fifty horse power gasoline engines drive her scant twenty-six feet of hull over the water at a speed of more than forty-two miles an hour.

headline.main: NEW MOTORBOAT BEATS WORLD'S RECORD IN SPEED
